<section class="section">
  <div class="container container--narrow">
    <h1 class="section__title mt-0">About Amara India</h1>
    <p class="section__subtitle mb-0" style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
      We’re building the next-generation global sourcing platform for Indian manufacturers—starting with sports and fitness, scaling to all of global trade.
    </p>

    <p style="font-size: 1.0625rem; line-height: 1.75; color: var(--color-text);">
      <strong>Amara India</strong> is the global sourcing gateway for Indian sports and fitness manufacturers. We connect international buyers—fitness brands, sports retailers, and ecommerce sellers—with verified Indian factories that produce gym equipment, cricket gear, yoga products, training equipment, and fitness accessories.
    </p>
    <p style="font-size: 1.0625rem; line-height: 1.75; color: var(--color-text);">
      Our long-term vision is to become the AI-powered platform for global trade from India. We’re starting with a focused vertical where India already leads: sports and fitness manufacturing. From here we’ll expand into handicrafts, sustainable products, wellness, textiles, and beyond—powered by verification, data, and AI.
    </p>
    <p style="font-size: 1.0625rem; line-height: 1.75; color: var(--color-text);">
      We’re not a directory. We’re a technology company building the infrastructure for transparent, efficient, and scalable sourcing—so buyers find the right suppliers and Indian manufacturers reach the right global markets.
    </p>

    <h2 style="font-size: 1.25rem; margin-top: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">What we offer today</h2>
    <ul style="color: var(--color-text); line-height: 1.8;">
      <li>Verified Indian sports and fitness manufacturers</li>
      <li>Transparent supplier profiles (MOQ, certifications, capacity)</li>
      <li>Direct factory access—no middlemen</li>
      <li>Export-ready suppliers</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 style="font-size: 1.25rem; margin-top: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">Where we’re headed</h2>
    <ul style="color: var(--color-text); line-height: 1.8;">
      <li>AI Supplier Match, Price Benchmarking, Demand Analyzer</li>
      <li>Expansion into more industries</li>
      <li>Data and intelligence for global trade</li>
    </ul>

    <p class="text-center" style="margin-top: 2rem;">
      <strong>Get in touch:</strong>
      <a href="mailto:team@amaraindia.com" style="margin-left: 0.5rem;">team@amaraindia.com</a>
    </p>
    <p class="text-center" style="margin-top: 1.5rem;">
      <%= link_to "Contact us", contact_path, class: "btn btn--primary" %>
      <%= link_to "Find manufacturers", products_path, class: "btn btn--secondary" %>
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
